    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >诺德要塞是一款专为追求高重玩性和无尽组合的策略爱好者量身打造的塔防游戏。建造、管理闲适的中世纪北欧村落，享受轻松上手的深入策略游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028310/extras/dddd266e19485e916f02e9e765d3dc9a.poster.avif?t=1769168791\" width=800 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028310/extras/dddd266e19485e916f02e9e765d3dc9a.webm?t=1769168791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028310/extras/dddd266e19485e916f02e9e765d3dc9a.mp4?t=1769168791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028310/extras/78efc7feb857f40fde0dd72c78c754ce.avif?t=1769168791\" width=800 height=90 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌控超过20座具有独特升级和元成长的建筑，体验多样化的战略发展选择，在经济增长和保卫家园之间求得完美平衡。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028310/extras/fe989a3231a081b0f59e30229d50f951.avif?t=1769168791\" width=800 height=90 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择9座具有独特能力、提供无数个性化选项的塔楼。精密调整战术，步步为营、牢不可破。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028310/extras/61ab468d0052ecc4da8b7e7d0a1f7192.poster.avif?t=1769168791\" width=800 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028310/extras/61ab468d0052ecc4da8b7e7d0a1f7192.webm?t=1769168791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028310/extras/61ab468d0052ecc4da8b7e7d0a1f7192.mp4?t=1769168791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028310/extras/1317cadfdaa5c50a9ed70076ca1865ef.avif?t=1769168791\" width=800 height=90 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索超过100种定制升级，体验丰富的个性化定制选项，增强战略纵深、开拓无数组合。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028310/extras/2cea9dd4325aff8863fa30ed3cb20368.poster.avif?t=1769168791\" width=800 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028310/extras/2cea9dd4325aff8863fa30ed3cb20368.webm?t=1769168791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028310/extras/2cea9dd4325aff8863fa30ed3cb20368.mp4?t=1769168791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028310/extras/0106a5c43b422ba2911464aaf4a99353.avif?t=1769168791\" width=800 height=90 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >哪位将军最适合保卫诺德要塞？在上百种英雄组合中遣兵调将！遗物能够给你带来大量增益，助你发展经济、加强防御。神谕则永远会给你一种不同的选择，例如：面对5波更强大的敌人并获取更丰厚的奖励，或者在接下来5波次中享受更低廉的塔楼造价？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028310/extras/09a6cddc6c9b4e7c0cfcac3baddf068f.avif?t=1769168791\" width=800 height=90 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >滚雪球效应也可以“滚”进现实。高明的决策会产生协同效应，让你在焰火般的视觉效果中光荣征服一波又一波日益强大的敌人以及领袖。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028310/extras/3bcbb3ca3fbce39a001e2b2becdb1d48.avif?t=1769168791\" width=800 height=90 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在排位系统中与好友一较高下，或者与全世界的玩家同台竞技。你能升到英灵殿排位吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028310/extras/b849b2e6a4d49bd2b55ebddfa2f33d38.poster.avif?t=1769168791\" width=800 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028310/extras/b849b2e6a4d49bd2b55ebddfa2f33d38.webm?t=1769168791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028310/extras/b849b2e6a4d49bd2b55ebddfa2f33d38.mp4?t=1769168791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
